Question 1: What does JVM stand for?
A) Java Virtual Machine
B) Java Very Main
C) Java Virtual Method
D) Java Viable Memory
Your answer (A/B/C/D): A

Question 2: What is the java source file extension?
A) .javaexe
B) .javas
C) .java
D) .exe
Your answer (A/B/C/D): C

Question 3: What are comments used for?
A) To tell the compiler what it needs to do
B) To close a line of code
C) To keep reminders and notes
D) To define the scope of the class
Your answer (A/B/C/D): C

